Txtlocal,is,a,service,that,provides,group,text,messaging,for,individual,use,marketing,and,advertising,purposes,or,other,functions,such,as,appointment,reminders,Pricing,is,dependent,on,the,number,of,texts,so,customers,can,use,Txtlocal,for,either,a,small,group,of,people,or,large,depending,on,their,needs,The,Txtlocal,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,Txtlocal,information,and,functionality,into,other,sites,and,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,sending,text,messages,receiving,text,messages,and,checking,credit,balances